Subject: To the Battle.
From: "Carnage Blood" <Carnage@...>

** Vlad exited the Iron Fist, immediately looking beyond his position and towards the edges of the island, Shesta with her snout to the ground at his heels.  There was a pull, an urge to leave and travel in the direction the remainder of the Alliance had gone. To the Maximal base.  So without hesitation he began to cross the area between the sea and himself.**
